divs: sighting detailsstood outside apartment with dog on leash,talking with wife and neighbor who was on her balcony on a second level. i walked five feet out in the grass and looked up at the stars on a clear night and was mesmarized by a faint grey outline of an object hardly noticable. two seconds pass and i'm certain the object was not a flock of geese. it's shape was that similar. three second pass and i instinctively take my eyes off it to reconfirm its position and at four seconds i see it folling the same course and speed heading directly towards the moon!! maybe now i'll surely see the object more clearly with the moon as a backdrop. but a five seconds it was directly above me and it just either absorbed the stars or completely disappeared. i think what little reflection i did see was due the moon light off the edge of the obect. this sign is exactly and i'm certain the shape and ufo i seen { if you can enlarge that sign to 1 and a 1\2 feet then thats the length too.
